-- marts/ — Analytics-ready business models
-- Final tables consumed by Grafana dashboards and ad-hoc queries.
-- Naming convention: fct_<fact>.sql  /  dim_<dimension>.sql
-- Examples:
--   fct_race_results.sql      (one row per driver per race)
--   fct_pit_stops.sql         (one row per pit stop)
--   dim_drivers.sql           (slowly changing driver dimension)
--   dim_circuits.sql          (circuit dimension)
--   dim_constructors.sql      (team/constructor dimension)
